org.llrp.ltk.generated.custom.messages

Class IMPINJ_SAVE_SETTINGS_RESPONSE

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.llrp.ltk.types.LLRPMessage
      • org.llrp.ltk.generated.custom.messages.IMPINJ_SAVE_SETTINGS_RESPONSE

  • public class IMPINJ_SAVE_SETTINGS_RESPONSE
extends LLRPMessage
    This custom message is the response by the Reader to an IMPINJ_SAVE_SETTINGS message. If the Reader was capable of saving the current configuration to persistent storage, the Reader returns the success code in the LLRPStatus parameter. If there is an error, the Reader returns an appropriate error code. See also
